  "remarks": "Appointed the SPLA-IO’s Deputy Chief of Staff for Operations on December\n21, 2014. Forces under his command targeted civilians, including women, in April 2014\nduring an assault on Bentiu, including targeted killings on the basis of\nethnicity. INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice web link:https://www.interpol.int/en/How-we-work/Notices/View-UN-Notices-Individuals",
